SELECT 
       [PrcCode]
      ,[PrcName]
      ,[DimCode]
      ,[U_Owner]
      ,[U_PorfApp]
      ,[U_OwnerMail]
      ,[U_Secondary]
      ,[U_SecMail]
      ,[U_PorfApp2]
      ,[Active]
      ,T0.[ValidTo]
      ,T0.u_porf
       ,DB_NAME() [DB_NAME]
 FROM [dbo].OPRC  t0 inner join [dbo].OACT T1 on t0.PrcCode= t1.U_PORF_Dep OR T0.PrcCode=T1.U_PORF_Alloc
 
 where Active <> 'N' AND T1.U_PORF='Y'
 GROUP BY 
     [PrcCode]
      ,[PrcName]
      ,[DimCode]
      ,[U_Owner]
      ,[U_PorfApp]
      ,[U_OwnerMail]
      ,[U_Secondary]
      ,[U_SecMail]
      ,[U_PorfApp2]
      ,[Active]
      ,T0.[ValidTo]
      ,T0.u_porf
